summary: An Ordinance authorizing the Mayor and City Comptroller to issue Local Improvement Bonds for the improvement of the Northeasterly Forty feet of Raveuna Blvd. between Woodlawn Avenue and the angle point near 9th Avenue N.E. in the City of Seattle., by grading under Ordinance No. 23088, creating Local Improvement District No. 2251 prescribing the rate of interest thereon and authorizing their delivery to the contractor constructing the improvement.
